{"id":"lyr_5Y2r5YWw_NDIw_0006","text":"誰和你拍拖很可畏","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":8},"semantics":{"themes":["關係的恐懼","不確定"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["誰","拍拖","可畏"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,5,4,3,9,9,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["seoi4","wo4","nei5","paak3","to1","han2","ho2","wai3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"誰","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"和","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"拍拖","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"很","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"可畏","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"「誰和你拍拖」是反問句，帶有質疑和不安，而「很可畏」則直接表達了對這段關係的恐懼。"},"source":{"title":"拍錯拖","artists":["衛蘭"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_420","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y2r5YWw_NDIw_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y2r5YWw_NDIw_0007","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
