{"id":"lyr_5Y2r5YWw_NDIw_0035","text":"只想有日有可能等到你肯改過","structure":{"line_index":35,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["期望","等待","改變"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["只想","可能","等到","改過"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[9,9,5,2,5,9,0,9,4,5,9,9,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zi2","soeng2","jau5","jat6","jau5","ho2","nang4","dang2","dou3","nei5","hang2","goi2","gwo3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"只想","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"有","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"日","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"有","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"可能","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"等到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"肯","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"改過","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「只想」表達了主角的唯一願望，而「有可能等到你肯改過」則是一種渺茫但持續的期望。"},"source":{"title":"拍錯拖","artists":["衛蘭"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_420","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y2r5YWw_NDIw_0034","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y2r5YWw_NDIw_0036","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y2r5YWw_NDIw_0036","text":"如未答應 至少每夜想起我","structure":{"line_index":36,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["最低期望","思念","妥協"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["至少","想起"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,4,4,5,2,9,9,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jyu4","mei6","daap3","zi3","mui5","je6","soeng2","hei2","ngo5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"如未","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"答應","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"至少","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"每夜","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"想起","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"「如未答應」是假設，而「至少」則表達了主角退而求其次的最低期望，即「想起」。這裏的「想起」比「陪伴」更為被動。"},"source":{"title":"拍錯拖","artists":["衛蘭"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_420","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y2r5YWw_NDIw_0035","next_line_id":null,"paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
